  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>While wearing medium or heavy armor, you may divert any damage taken from falling to your armor. Damage you redirect this way ignores your armor&#8217;s hardness, and you are still knocked prone if you would have taken fall damage without this talent. You suffer any damage in excess of your armor&#8217;s hit points. <strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Cushioning Armor</p>\n<p><strong>Addendum:</strong> You may select this talent a second time. When you use this talent, creatures within 5 feet of where you land suffer bludgeoning damage equal to half the damage that would be dealt to your armor. [Apoc: Armor Talents 2]</p>\n",
